Control._Name: Set All Components to New or Pre-Existing
Please note that a selection will change the status of ALL components  in the current design.
Warning!!!  Deleting a floor plan page will delete all objects existing on that page.  Are you sure you want to proceed?
Please note that paths used in any antenna configuration CANNOT BE DELETED.

NOTE:  Modified defaults will apply to new 
RF Devices added to the design, and will
not change the values of existing RF Devices.
Be sure to hit Enter or Tab after modifying
any of the defaults.

NOTE:  To bring IR and RF devices to the
front of cables on a 101 page, click
the Select By Type button, select
Layer>{No Layer}>OK, then click the
Bring to Front button.  Cables and imported
floor plans will be excluded from selection.

Closets with IR or RF devices assigned to
them will not be listed.
